front.title: •Darth Maul With Lightsaber
front.gametext: Permanent weapon is •Maul's Double-Bladed Lightsaber (twice per battle, may target a character for free; draw two destiny; target 'hit,' and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value).

combo: Darth Maul With Lightsaber + Maul Strikes
Darth Maul With Lightsaber + The Phantom Menace While present with an opponent's Jedi, Maul is defense value +2 and immune to attrition.
Darth Maul With Lightsaber + I Have You Now Add one battle destiny (two if Rebel is Luke) if a Dark Jedi and a Rebel with ability > 2 are involved in the same battle.
Darth Maul With Lightsaber + Force Field Cancels an attempt to target a Dark Jedi with a character weapon.
Darth Maul With Lightsaber + Gamall Wironicc Gamall Wironicc protects characters present with him from the targeting of a weapon.
Darth Maul With Lightsaber + Chokk Chokk prevents your characters present with him from having their forfeit value reduced.
